OL,3,CBelfast hero describes fighting off
OL,4,Cknifeman with son's hurling stick
OL,6,FThe pair both jumped out of the
OL,7,Fvehicle to help, with Tighearnan
OL,8,Fgrabbing his son's hurling stick from
OL,9,Fthe boot and using it to try stop the
OL,10,Fattacker from stabbing Ogilvy.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FFootage of the attack showed
OL,18,FTighearnan swinging the stick at the
OL,19,Fknifeman alongside two other men
OL,20,Fbefore the police arrived at the scene.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
