OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781179881
OL,3,CBelfast hero describes fighting off
OL,4,Cknifeman with son's hurling stick
OL,6,F"At the end of the day, there's a man
OL,7,Flying there. I just heard he's being
OL,8,Fstabbed. There was blood everywhere,
OL,9,Fso the first thing is that man needs
OL,10,Fhelp," Tighearnan told Good Morning
OL,11,FBritain about the incident.
OL,13,F"It's a natural reaction for what I
OL,14,Ffeel is me, and most people who I know
OL,15,Fwould also do the same from where we
OL,16,Fgrew up. It was just that type of
OL,17,Fmentality."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
