OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781179881
OL,3,CBelfast hero describes fighting off
OL,4,Cknifeman with son's hurling stick
OL,6,FSuspect Hadi Alodid has been charged
OL,7,Fwith attempted murder over the attack,
OL,8,Fas well as threats to kill an NHS
OL,9,Fradiographer and possession of a knife.
OL,11,FThe Sudanese national appeared before
OL,12,FBelfast Magistrates' Court on
OL,13,FWednesday morning and was remanded
OL,14,Finto custody until his next court
OL,15,Fappearance in four weeks.
OL,17,FOgilvie lost his left eye and suffered
OL,18,Fother injuries in the attack, but is
OL,19,Fin a stable condition, his family have
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
