OL,3,CBelfast hero describes fighting off
OL,4,Cknifeman with son's hurling stick
OL,6,FA fundraising page set up by stranger
OL,7,FNiall Donnan to buy Tighearnan a pint
OL,8,Fhas attracted almost #30,000 in
OL,9,Fdonations, which he said would be
OL,10,Fshared with Ogilvy and his family.
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland has seen two nights
OL,13,Fof unrest following the attack, with
OL,14,Fmultiple people arrested and several
OL,15,Fofficers injured.
OL,17,FPolice used water cannons on rioters
OL,18,Fand officers were pelted with bricks
OL,19,Fand petrol bombs in Co Antrim, on the
OL,20,Foutskirts of Belfast, on Wednesday
OL,21,Fevening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
